org.dspace.content

Class Metadatum

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dspace.content.Metadatum

  • public class Metadatum
extends Object
    Simple data structure-like class representing a flat metadata value. It has a schema, element, qualifier, value, language and authority.
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
    Robert Tansley, Martin Hald
